Design UI fpr 7 Wonders:


1. Card display - displays cards that you are able to buy
2. Wonder display - displays your wonder and associated info such as upgrade level etc.
3. Scrap heap/Trash can/bank - Target for throwing/selling cards.
4. Display of already bought cards.
5. Display of neighbouring cities.
6. Display of other cities need to be taken into consideration as well, although no interaction is possible.

7. Mouse interaction:
- Click and hold to move a card.
- Release button when card is in target area triggers the move.
- Click on "end turn" to commit change.
- Click on "Undo" to Undo
- Mouse over a card to see the cost of the card (and its options, OR better still, show cost


